A tool to execute perf on a set of given machines in AWS

Given a list of instances, amis, or security groups, or..?
It will setup and install perf on all machines.
Start system-wide profiling as root
When you hit ctrl+c (or after the specified time)
all profiling will be stopped
(optionally) the results of all profiling can be downloaded to the local machine
alternatively, we could support downloading to another machine for analysis



